You spent all day filming, where was Sheng Jingchu?

101
00:08:00,450 --> 00:08:02,260
He doesn't go back often.

102
00:08:02,260 --> 00:08:04,110
- How about Xie Hanzhou?
- Wasn't there.

103
00:08:04,110 --> 00:08:07,550
Cheng Liao, I'm telling you. You might be close to VP Xu,

104
00:08:07,550 --> 00:08:09,610
you're also Sheng Jingchu's girlfriend,

105
00:08:09,610 --> 00:08:11,600
but I'm the one who supervises the production.

106
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:14,460
I'm accountable to the vice president for it!

107
00:08:14,460 --> 00:08:18,030
If the program isn't good, neither VP Xu, Sheng Jingchu,

108
00:08:18,030 --> 00:08:21,400
or even your sister can protect you!

109
00:08:21,400 --> 00:08:23,300
Get out!

110
00:08:28,420 --> 00:08:30,500
Auntie Liu went crazy again?

111
00:08:31,080 --> 00:08:33,190
Is my video really that bad?

112
00:08:33,190 --> 00:08:35,980
It's good, but it's not what Auntie Liu wants.

113
00:08:35,980 --> 00:08:41,050
She wants to find the stain on a piece of white paper, something that gets views and clicks.

114
00:08:41,050 --> 00:08:43,910
Is this how my work is always going to be?

115
00:08:43,910 --> 00:08:46,870
Every day to think of different ways to deceive viewers.

116
00:08:46,870 --> 00:08:49,810
I'm now being criticized because I'm sharing the truth.

117
00:08:50,560 --> 00:08:53,960
Take it slow and get used to it, you'll accept it eventually.

118
00:08:54,750 --> 00:08:57,150
I can't accept it.

119
00:08:57,150 --> 00:09:00,350
Keep your "never give up spirit" at work.

120
00:09:00,350 --> 00:09:01,810
Never give up,

121
00:09:01,810 --> 00:09:06,930
