122
00:09:14,700 --> 00:09:16,830
Take that to cure what ails you!

123
00:09:22,110 --> 00:09:23,560
[Binhai Television]

124
00:09:23,560 --> 00:09:27,180
I know I won't be with Cheng Yi Conversation for long,

125
00:09:27,180 --> 00:09:32,270
I want to reserve the rest of the episodes to the Sihai Jiuzhou Cup Four Countries Invitational GO Tournament.
